dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Jonathan Murphy. May I have your name, please?
Nice to meet you, Catherine. How do you spell your last name?
Great, thank you. Can you provide me with the VIN (Vehicle Identification Number) of the vehicle involved in the incident?
Sure, it's one zero zero G as in golf, F as in foxtrot, Z as in zulu, six Y as in yankee R as in romeo.
Thank you, Catherine. Could you also confirm the date of the incident in the format month day year?
It was zero six dash one four dash two zero two two.
Thank you for providing the information, Catherine. We'll process your claim and keep you updated. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, that's all. Thank you for your help.
You're welcome, Catherine. Thank you for reaching out to Old Stone Auto Insurance. Have a great day!
